LessonsLearned:
&lt;b&gt;Measures to prevent recurrence: &lt;/b&gt;When the Original Report was prepared the situation was under examination by the competent authorities. It is believed preventive measures will also be taken for similar installations, which may include:
&lt;br&gt;1- the improvement of the internal safety organization;
&lt;br&gt;2- the installation of sensors for monitor the concentration of dangerous substances in the air, connected with alarm systems;
&lt;br&gt;3- setting up of work-permit procedures;
&lt;br&gt;4- the use of well-trained personnel.&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;b&gt;Measures to mitigate consequences: &lt;/b&gt;Locating plants at a safe distance from other activities.
